headline.print_headline: Hamilton Fastest as Mercedes Dominate U.S. Practice
headline.main: Hamilton Fastest as Mercedes Dominate U.S. Practice

lead_paragraph: Formula One championship leader Lewis Hamilton and his title rival team mate Nico Rosberg were separated by mere fumes on Friday in a familiar Mercedes one-two in U.S. Grand Prix practice.
